function 'Context.ShowFullMonth' = ```
		
		// Function that returns the total value for a full month.
		// - Example: To get the full-month Budget
		(
		    // The measure or expression to return for the full month.
		    // - Example: [Budget]
		    ValueToAdjust: ANYREF
		)
		=>
		    CALCULATE (
		        ValueToAdjust,
		        ALL ( 'Date' ),
		        VALUES (
		            'Date'[Calendar Month Year (ie Jan 21)]
		        )
		    )
		
		```
