function 'RLS.ApplyRLS' = ```
		
		// Function to apply RLS based on an employee security table
		(
		    // The table that contains employee information used to set up dynamic RLS
		    employeeSecurityTable: ANYREF,
		    
		    // The column that has the employee email that matches USERPRINCIPALNAME()
		    employeeEmailColumn: ANYREF,
		    
		    // The column that has the employee name in the security table
		    employeeNameColumn: ANYREF,
		    
		    // The column that has the employee name in the dimension table
		    dimensionEmployeeNameColumn: SCALAR
		)
		=>
		    VAR _CurrentUser =
		        SELECTCOLUMNS (
		            FILTER (
		                employeeSecurityTable,
		                employeeEmailColumn = USERPRINCIPALNAME ( )
		            ),
		            "@Name", employeeNameColumn
		        )
		    RETURN
		        dimensionEmployeeNameColumn IN _CurrentUser
		```
